Nonye is an AI performance coach who designs user interfaces using Pen and Paper, React, Electron, and TypeScript to build meaningful connections with her SWE audience. 
She leverages sentiment analysis to uncover monetizable patterns in SWE mindshare, establishing the groundwork for multimodal AI in peer-to-peer advertising. 
Her research focuses on applying reinforcement learning techniques to resolve feature visibility and cognitive resource allocation challenges to enable seamless connection and disconnection cycles during user research and testing of always-on AI.
